headline: New ONEOK Directors Add Governance Focus To Capital Allocation Story
summary: ONEOK appointed Mark A. McCollum and Precious Williams Owodunni as new independent directors to its board. The appointments add additional industry, executive, and governance experience to ONEOK's oversight structure. Investors are watching how the refreshed board may influence future priorities and oversight at NYSE:OKE.
